---
import { ArrowUpRight } from "@lucide/astro";
---

<div class="section-wrapper dark-bg">
  <section
    class="dark-bg flex flex-col w-full items-center border-x border-white-line"
  >
    <header
      id="Testimonies"
      class="section-header section-margin-top border-y border-white-line scroll-mt-16"
    >
      <h2
        class="font-bold text-3xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl leading-tight text-left text-shadow-header-black"
      >
        From small freelance work to enterprise software projects.
      </h2>
    </header>
    <div class="section-margin-bottom grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2">
      <article
        class="flex flex-col justify-between p-6 lg:p-8 gap-4 lg:gap-6 border-b border-white-line"
      >
        <p class="text-lg lg:text-xl italic leading-relaxed">
          “My wild style needed a different approach, a website that matched
          such energy. Javier was able to understand this and deliver a
          completely unique product.”
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-8 justify-between">
          <a
            class="flex items-center whitespace-nowrap"
            rel="external"
            href="https://kennethandersonx.com/"
            target="_blank"
          >
            <span class="font-medium lg:text-lg">Case Study</span>
            <ArrowUpRight class="w-5 h-5" />
          </a>
          <p class="font-light text-sm lg:text-base italic text-right">
            Kenneth Anderson, Photographer
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article
        class="flex flex-col justify-between p-6 lg:p-8 gap-5 lg:gap-6 md:border-l border-b border-white-line"
      >
        <p class="text-lg lg:text-xl italic leading-relaxed">
          “Javier started working with us to help our IT team in our different
          e-commerce stores. We developed a long-lasting relationship and he
          always delivered on time and with high quality.”
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-8 justify-between">
          <a
            class="flex items-center whitespace-nowrap"
            rel="nofollow external"
            href="https://hochzeitshaus.berlin/"
            target="_blank"
          >
            <span class="font-medium lg:text-lg">Case Study</span>
            <ArrowUpRight class="w-5 h-5" />
          </a>
          <p class="font-light text-sm lg:text-base italic text-right">
            CM Wedding GmbH
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>
      <div></div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
